name: alloc::collections::btree::node::Handle::<collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Mut<'a>, K, V, NodeType>, HandleType>::reborrow_mut
doc:
Temporarily takes out another mutable handle on the same location. Beware, as
 this method is very dangerous, doubly so since it might not immediately appear
 dangerous.

 For details, see `NodeRef::reborrow_mut`.
